    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link
        href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Nunito:wght@300;400;600;700&family=Playfair+Display:wght@400;700&display=swap"
        rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">
</head>

<body>
    <!-- Energy Banner -->
    <div class="energy-banner">
        <div class="container">
            <p>üöÄ <strong>Ready to level up?</strong> Join our weekend trekking group this Saturday! <a
                    href="/activities">Sign Up Now</a></p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <nav class="navbar">
        <div class="container">
            <h1 class="logo">MINDHAVEN <span class="dot">.</span></h1>
            <ul class="nav-links">
                <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
                <li><a href="/about">About</a></li>
                <li><a href="/j">Health Topics</a></li>
                <li><a href="/activities">Adventures</a></li>
                <li><a href="/activities" class="btn-action">Get Started</a></li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <header id="home" class="hero">
        <div class="hero-overlay"></div>
        <div class="hero-content">
            <span class="badge-energy">It's a New Day</span>
            <h1>RECHARGE.<br>RECONNECT.<br>RISE.</h1>
            <p class="hero-lead">Life isn't meant to be lived on the sidelines. Break through the noise, find your
                people, and discover what makes you feel <strong>alive</strong>.</p>
            <div class="hero-btns">
                <a href="/activities" class="btn-primary">Find Your Adventure</a>
                <a href="#community" class="btn-transparent">Meet The Tribe</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </header>

    <section id="features" class="power-section">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="section-header">
                <h2>Fuel Your Soul</h2>
                <p>Don't just survive. Thrive. Here is your toolkit for a boundless life.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="power-grid">
                <div class="power-card">
                    <div class="card-icon">üî•</div>
                    <h3>Ignite Your Passion</h3>
                    <p>Discover hobbies that set your soul on fire. From painting to rock climbing, find your flow
                        state.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="power-card">
                    <div class="card-icon">‚ö°</div>
                    <h3>Physical Power</h3>
                    <p>Move your body, change your mind. High-energy group workouts, treks, and yoga sessions.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="power-card">
                    <div class="card-icon">ü§ù</div>
                    <h3>Real Connection</h3>
                    <p>No small talk. Deep conversations with people who truly get it. Build your circle.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="challenges" class="challenge-section">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-half text-col">
                    <h2>Conquer Your Mountains</h2>
                    <p>Everyone faces obstacles. It's how you climb them that matters. We give you the gear to reach the
                        summit.</p>

                    <div class="challenge-list">
                        <div class="challenge-item">
                            <div class="c-icon"><i class="fas fa-fist-raised"></i></div>
                            <div class="c-text">
                                <h4>Crush Anxiety</h4>
                                <p>Turn nervous energy into excitement. Learn practical tools to own the room.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="challenge-item">
                            <div class="c-icon"><i class="fas fa-sun"></i></div>
                            <div class="c-text">
                                <h4>Beat the Blues</h4>
                                <p>Small steps lead to giant leaps. rediscovering color in a gray world.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="challenge-item">
                            <div class="c-icon"><i class="fas fa-brain"></i></div>
                            <div class="c-text">
                                <h4>Master Your Mind</h4>
                                <p>You are the captain. Learn mindfulness techniques to steer your ship.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-half visual-col">
                    <div class="visual-stack">
                        <div class="img-card card-1"
                            style="background-image: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1526772662000-3f88f107f5d8?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=80')">
                        </div>
                        <div class="img-card card-2"
                            style="background-image: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1500964757637-c85e8a162699?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=80')">
                        </div>
                        <div class="floating-badge">
                            <span>100%</span>
                            <small>Possibility</small>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="community" class="vibe-section">
        <div class="container text-center">
            <h2>Join The Movement</h2>
            <p>Our community is active, welcoming, and waiting for you.</p>

            <div class="vibe-grid">
                <a href="/activities" class="vibe-card">
                    <div class="vibe-bg"
                        style="background-image: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1523580494863-6f3031224c94?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=80')">
                    </div>
                    <div class="vibe-content">
                        <h3>Music Jams</h3>
                        <span>Every Friday</span>
                    </div>
                </a>
                <a href="/activities" class="vibe-card">
                    <div class="vibe-bg"
                        style="background-image: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1471943311424-646960669fbc?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=80')">
                    </div>
                    <div class="vibe-content">
                        <h3>Sunrise Yoga</h3>
                        <span>Every Morning</span>
                    </div>
                </a>
                <a href="/activities" class="vibe-card">
                    <div class="vibe-bg"
                        style="background-image: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1533240332313-0db49b459ad6?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=80')">
                    </div>
                    <div class="vibe-content">
                        <h3>Game Nights</h3>
                        <span>Wednesdays</span>
                    </div>
                </a>
            </div>

            <a href="/activities" class="btn-primary btn-large">Explore All Events</a>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="wisdom" class="motivation-slider">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="section-title">Words of Power</h2>

            <div class="quote-slider-container">
                <button class="slider-btn prev-btn"><i class="fas fa-chevron-left"></i></button>
                <div class="quote-slider-track">
                    <div class="quote-slide active">
                        <div class="quote-content">
                            <blockquote>"The only impossible journey is the one you never begin."</blockquote>
                            <cite>‚Äî Tony Robbins</cite>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="quote-slide">
                        <div class="quote-content">
                            <blockquote>"Don't watch the clock; do what it does. Keep going."</blockquote>
                            <cite>‚Äî Sam Levenson</cite>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="quote-slide">
                        <div class="quote-content">
                            <blockquote>"Your life does not get better by chance, it gets better by change."
                            </blockquote>
                            <cite>‚Äî Jim Rohn</cite>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <!-- New Quotes -->
                    <div class="quote-slide">
                        <div class="quote-content">
                            <blockquote>"Believe you can and you're halfway there."</blockquote>
                            <cite>‚Äî Theodore Roosevelt</cite>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="quote-slide">
                        <div class="quote-content">
                            <blockquote>"Act as if what you do makes a difference. It does."</blockquote>
                            <cite>‚Äî William James</cite>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="quote-slide">
                        <div class="quote-content">
                            <blockquote>"What lies behind us and what lies before us are tiny matters compared to what
                                lies within us."</blockquote>
                            <cite>‚Äî Ralph Waldo Emerson</cite>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="quote-slide">
                        <div class="quote-content">
                            <blockquote>"It always seems impossible until it's done."</blockquote>
                            <cite>‚Äî Nelson Mandela</cite>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="quote-slide">
                        <div class="quote-content">
                            <blockquote>"Happiness is not something ready made. It comes from your own actions."
                            </blockquote>
                            <cite>‚Äî Dalai Lama</cite>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <button class="slider-btn next-btn"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i></button>
            </div>
            <div class="slider-dots">
                <span class="dot active" data-slide="0"></span>
                <span class="dot" data-slide="1"></span>
                <span class="dot" data-slide="2"></span>
                <span class="dot" data-slide="3"></span>
                <span class="dot" data-slide="4"></span>
                <span class="dot" data-slide="5"></span>
                <span class="dot" data-slide="6"></span>
                <span class="dot" data-slide="7"></span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

